Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.03,0:00:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.77,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.14,0:00:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生奈落\N在白灵山被发现重要的分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对桔梗毫不留情地下了毒手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个悲剧\N唤醒了我们心灵的灰暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导我们\N走进奈落布下的新陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.78,0:00:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.05,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.32,0:00:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.13,0:00:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.10,0:00:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.10,0:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.14,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.11,0:00:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.15,0:01:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.09,0:01:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.10,0:01:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.87,0:01:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.08,0:01:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.15,0:01:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.06,0:01:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.99,0:02:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落这个家伙\N难道就为了杀一个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但布下了\N天罗地网般的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把自己关在山上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗姑娘\N并不是普通的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.04,0:02:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落害怕的是\N桔梗姑娘的灵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而奈落一直想除掉自己的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.91,0:02:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉那颗\N仰慕桔梗的人类的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.62,0:02:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落也曾经\N一度想摆脱人类的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个拥有\N强盗鬼蜘蛛的心和记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个叫无双的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.49,0:02:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.93,0:02:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括身体  还有力量\N全部都给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.69,0:03:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个无双
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来还是再度\N成为奈落身体的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许当时时机还太早吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.30,0:03:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这份执着  这股欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说  奈落他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在白灵山上见到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些数量庞大的肉球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.72,0:03:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些就是\N他用来封闭消除人类的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造新生肉体的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.96,0:03:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.91,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总括来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.67,0:04:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决了那个碍事的巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后\N就可以安心地为所欲为吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过\N我一定会阻止他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我也该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.69,0:04:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走咯  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要多多保重哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙你也别太逞强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.94,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭笨狗怎么没来打扰我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说也奇怪\N那笨蛋跑哪去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.08,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还带着张\N非常愁云惨雾的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然扔下戈薇不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己出去找桔梗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.22,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来犬夜叉还不能\N接受桔梗姑娘的死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他的心情我可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.59,0:05:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第125话 戈薇的心灵暗处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要自己对付那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不等我陪你一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冲进河里瘴气也不会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.40,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定在这里吧  桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那个女人是什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害桔梗的\N是奈落那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着她死却没办法救她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.66,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落就由我来解决他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不必\N那么辛苦地战斗下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见你这个样子\N我终于明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要奈落\N还有一颗鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就代表他有弱点存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我就可以除掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他永远永远\N离开这个人世间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.77,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗从来没有相信过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗  你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.29,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的\N一个人孤零零死去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.73,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.30,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个\N还慢吞吞的干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶着去追奈落呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有股强大的邪气往南走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先往北然后又回到南边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就在南边等\N不就好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在犬夜叉不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是好好亲近\N戈薇大姐的绝佳机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然就这样白白放过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂他在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.39,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要代替犬夜叉\N找到奈落把他给宰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我的好消息  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天已经亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底去哪里找桔梗了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你终于回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一夜没睡  一直在等我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.84,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问你…还没找到桔梗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要让我找到尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本是这么想的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么安慰他才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不想看到犬夜叉\N这副失魂落魄的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起让你担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…不要紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看犬夜叉的样子\N根本就是口是心非嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底该怎么做才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然连这一带都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受到白灵山崩塌的影响吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得新太郎他们的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃一点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弥勒法师跟戈薇姑娘你们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都平安无事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多村子都被妖怪给毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.88,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很庆幸\N新太郎他们都平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但犬夜叉他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那件事后一直很难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一路\N都在寻找逃脱的奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉已经离开白灵山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.83,0:10:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犬夜叉…真的放下了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.57,0:10:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实他内心深处\N还是想找桔梗的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么恐怖的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说是不是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说白灵山\N不过转眼间就崩塌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再发生什么重大悲剧就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股邪气是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可恶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是村子里第三起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.52,0:11:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下一些妖怪喽罗的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是那些\N从白灵山结界逃出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群妖怪们干的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  为什么会这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想对奈落\N穷追猛打查出真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但造成的后果\N却比之前更严重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.18,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连桔梗都送了命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒  我摘了一些花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托放那边好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来真是灾情惨重呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.03,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从白灵山那边来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.30,0:12:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫僧一向四海为家到处修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有座神圣的白灵山崩塌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一股邪气流窜到南边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到果真如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那天碰见的巫女说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.68,0:12:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是两天前的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山的另一边的小镇河滩上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个受伤的巫女被水冲到那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说是个叫奈落的下的毒手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说非要找到那个奈落不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是桔梗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.93,0:12:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我看她的伤势很严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已经没命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.61,0:13:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.75,0:13:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在犹豫些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快点去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗她一定在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不查清楚桔梗是死是活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本…没办法继续前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉还没有回来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我们还是先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉的话\N只要闻到戈薇的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快会追上来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么穿着奇装异服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇装异服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是说戈薇身上的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这个地方\N接二连三发生一些怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头交代\N发现可疑的人马上带进城里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要冲过去是挺容易的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用犬夜叉那套行不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且照我看\N这几个衙差只不过是凡人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此随时都可以逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们交头接耳在说些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们绑起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得马上把犬夜叉那家伙\N找回来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你放过我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不是什么可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上还带着通行证呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.28,0:14:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我斩\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们也会被杀吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子说什么都没有用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候不能再袖手旁观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.20,0:15:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来  小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是夫人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光叫我一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.38,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人我用不着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你在哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗死了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是唯一能看见\N四魂之玉碎片的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那个老师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的快受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要我抱个小鬼跑来跑去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.66,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个老师父是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我用尸舞操控的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.81,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来\N桔梗还活着是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会来救你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师跟驱魔师\N都被城里的人杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话的并不是那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他不会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他\N正发了疯似的到处找桔梗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个婴儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈落的分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个婴儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是在白灵山制造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底打算怎么样处置我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚不是说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.32,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是唯一能看见\N四魂之玉碎片的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你的这对眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.04,0:17:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都给我上西天去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然藏了暗器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个臭丫头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太嚣张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上给我抓住她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿回我们的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  看你们往哪跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.68,0:18:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙不难应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是\N听从上头命令的人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不能动手杀了这些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又是以寡敌众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.26,0:18:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来需要点时间对付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是戈薇一个人被带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.67,0:19:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快去救她的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那一对眼睛\N就留下来给我用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.79,0:19:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开戈薇身上的绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在怕什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为我会挖你的眼珠吃了你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样\N这个女人的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然找不到一点黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.09,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人类的心灵深处\N都会有黑暗的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒  憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有这种讨厌的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.70,0:20:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像有人\N正在探索我的内心似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.71,0:20:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉他不会来了
